When I add new table with Name "jitapi007f" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitapi007f" display
When I add new column with Name "jitapicol007f" Type "string" for Table name "jitapi007f"
When I navigate to menu "API endpoints" with submenu "API endpoints editor"
Then I should see API screen display
When I create new group API with name "groupapi007f"

When I select api name "groupapi007f" from list
When I add new API endpoint
When I set method of API to value "DELETE" in floating panel
